Package finalProject

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Correction
    This class should fix errors in the navigation program of the robot.
    Defense
    This class is the parallel class to Forward which will be called in the event that the robot is told to play defense during a certain round.
    Forward
    The Forward class is the controlling class which will be called after the initial localization process of the robot has been completed.
    Launcher
    This class is used to perform the launching of the ball toward the goal once it has reached the forward line and is situated directly in front of the target.
    Localization
    The class runs before either forward or defense are called and is used to set an original position for the robot.
    LocalizationFilter  
    Navigation
    The navigator is used to change either the robot's position or heading in a controlled manner.
    Odometer
    The odometer is the class that is used to continuously update the position of the robot based on the movement across the field of play.
    OdometryDisplay
    The odometry display should display to the screen what the current position of the robot is (based off of the odometer at the current moment).
    PController
    The obstacle avoidance class for the robot.
    UltrasonicPoller
    This class is used to intake the values from the ultrasonic sensor continually.
    WiFiExample
    Example class using WifiConnection to communicate with a server and receive data concerning the competition such as the starting corner the robot is placed in.
